I'm Going Home;;68;;96;;NC;;Elderly actor Gilbert Valence (Michel Piccoli) steps offstage after a performance and is told that his wife, his daughter and his son-in-law have all been killed in a horrific auto accident. Time passes, and Gilbert, now the guardian of his orphaned grandson, struggles to hold on to the small meaningful routines of his life. After taking a role in a film directed by American John Crawford (John Malkovich), he considers how to manage the end of his career.;;Drama,Comedy;;Manoel de Oliveira;;2001;;Michel Piccoli,Antoine Chappey,Catherine Deneuve,John Malkovich,Leonor Baldaque,Leonor Silveira;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/im_going_home